match.name: New Years Qualifier Match
match.about: PRS regional qualifier match for Rocky Mountain South division. Address for location of the match will be available upon registration. $50 match fee can be paid to PayPal at tg.balderree@yahoo.com or Venmo to @Tanner-Balderree.
